filling my heart♪

00:16:00.680 --> 00:16:03.920
♪That pure white is an endless longing♪

00:16:03.920 --> 00:16:07.570
♪The wind can't scatter the snow
it piles into a cocoon♪

00:16:07.780 --> 00:16:11.110
♪Trapping me in this winter♪

00:16:11.290 --> 00:16:14.660
♪Snow fills the city,
drifting toward the horizon♪

00:16:14.910 --> 00:16:18.470
♪Carrying away the sorrow of farewells♪

00:16:18.710 --> 00:16:22.300
♪I linger alone in the snow♪

00:16:22.300 --> 00:16:26.530
♪Waiting for a fate
that will never come♪